---
title: Crispy Noodle and Veggie Stir Fry with Ginger-Garlic Sauce
description: The key to this dish is leaving the noodles to crisp up in the pan long enough. It might be tempting to stir, but try to resist! A sweet, gingery sauce is kicked up by a touch of spicy Thai chili for heat.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/56a6e591f8b25e1f108b4568.jpg
